(62, 1, '2016-04-18 02:07:55', '2016-04-18 02:07:55', '<p><strong>Shipping</strong><br />\r\n<p>Please expect 2-3 working days for your item to be delivered if ordered <strong>locally</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>For International shipping, it would take 2-3 weeks due to customs policy.</p><br/>\r\n<p><strong>How To Return An Item</strong></p><br />\r\n<p>Your item must be in its original unused condition to be returned, unless there is a manufacturer defect. You must return the item within 30 days of your purchase. </p>\r\n<p>1. Please email info@yourstore.com to request a refund and we will assign you a tracking #.<br />\r\n2. Mail your returned item to:<br />\r\n     YourStore Name<br />\r\n     Returns Department Tracking #<br />\r\n     123 Your Store Road<br />\r\n     Store City, Store State Store Zip Code<br />\r\n3. Include in your package a signed letter stating the reason for your return and the original receipt. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Return Exceptions</strong><br />', 'Shipping and Returns', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shipping-returns', '', '', '2016-10-25 04:39:05', '2016-10-25 04:39:05', '', 0, 'http://taffen.co/?page_id=62', 0, 'page', '', 0),
