(66, 1, '2016-04-18 02:09:53', '2016-04-18 02:09:53', '<div class="term-conditions-container">\r\n<p>As part of accepting your transaction  and make a legal agreement without further reference to you, you must read these terms and condition to assure you that it contains all you need and for your satisfaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Please read and understand these Terms and Conditions:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>These terms and condition will apply when you place a transaction through TAFFEN PH.<br/>Please note that the Terms and Conditions from single transaction and multiple transactions differ on certain parts and it will be explained later in these terms.</li>\r\n<li>By ordering any of the products, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions; you can only purchase the product from the website if you are eligible to enter into a contract. If you are unable to understand, or have any questions about these terms kindly contact us <strong><a href="contact-us" target="_blank">here</a></strong><br/>\r\nYou are required to confirm and accept these terms before proceeding to any transaction.</li>\r\n<li>The terms do not affect your statutory rights.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Product</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The product descriptions are set out in the website, catalogues, brochures and other form of advertisement.</li>\r\n<li>In case of any product made to your special requirement, we required you to provide accurate information or specification; and is subject for confirmation.</li>\r\n<li>All product appearance on the website is subject to availability.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>3.Personal Information</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>When you create your TAFFEN account and place an order through the web site, you will be providing your personal information. You agree that TAFFEN may disclose personal information. TAFFEN will use your personal information to process your order and for the delivery of products ordered and other limited purposes.</li>\r\n<li>We retain and use all information strictly under Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n<li>We may contact you through email or other electronic communication once you agree on this.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong id="privacy_policy">4. Privacy Policy</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>This Privacy Policy set out to protect any information that you provide when you use this website for any transaction and other services. We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected and all the provided information including your name, address, email and any bank related/personal account is encrypted.</li>\r\n<li>We collect information from you when you register on our site and proceed for any transaction. By ordering, you are required to provide accurate detail to be used.</li>\r\n<li>Information use to improve Customer Service and process transaction successfully.</li>\r\n<li>We implement a variety of security measures for maintaining information safely. We further pledge never to sell this personal identifiable information to other, trade or transfer to outside parties.</li>\r\n<li>This online privacy policy applies only to information provided and collected through our website except information entered offline. By using our site, you agree to our Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>5. Order and Acceptance</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>When an order has been submitted it is subject for acceptance and may be reject for any reason. Although, we will notify you the reason within 24 hours.</li>\r\n<li>Conditions subject for order rejection: An error occurred on the webpage relating to the ordered product, price displayed description or availability of the product. </li>\r\n<li>The order process is set up on the website. Each step allows you to check and modify before submitting the order.</li>\r\n<li>After submitting the order, you will receive an email confirming receipt of your order (Order Confirmation).You must ensure that the Order Confirmation is correct and complete and inform us immediately for any error.</li>\r\n<li>You will receive an email when your order has been accepted.</li>\r\n<li>No variation of contract after Order Acceptance whether product description, Fees or otherwise can be made it after it has been entered into unless variation agreed by Customer and the company</li>\r\n<li>These Terms and Conditions apply only into a contract by you as a Customer. If you have any questions, comments or concerns regarding with the Order Acceptance policy, or if your order was rejected in error please contact us <strong><a href="contact-us" target="_blank">here</a></strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>6. Price and Payment </strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The product price and any additional delivery or other charges is indicated in the website when you place your order. No hidden charges.</li>\r\n<li>Prices and charges include VAT.</li>\r\n<li>The customers are subject to pay the bill after 5 working days from ordered date.</li>\r\n<li>Delivery will commence once payment has been validated. If you fail to pay within 5 working days, your order will be automatically “cancelled”.</li>\r\n<li>Payment methods are by Paypal (credit cards/debit cards) or bank deposit. All credit card holders are subject to validation checks and authorization by the card issuer. If the issuer of your payment card refuses to authorize payment to us, your order will not be accepted. Paypal or Bank Information will be sent during your transaction.</li>\r\n </ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>7. Order tracking</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>You can track the progress of your order by contacting us or sending email.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>8. Delivery</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>We will deliver the product to the Shipping Address provided by the customer within a week (local), 2-3 weeks international after the day of order is accepted, without any failing agreement, and/or undue delay on any event.</li>\r\n<li>In some cases, you will be informed in such territorial restrictions before you can purchase the product.</li>\r\n<li>Shipping and handling charges will depend on the value of your order and its destination on which product is being shipped.</li>\r\n<li>In such events has beyond our control or if we cannot deliver the products on time, you can end the Contract if;\r\n<br/>\r\nWe have refused to deliver the product due from incomplete information, product availability, weather and other unforeseen circumstances. After we fail to deliver on time,  we will specify a new date of delivery if you still want to continue your order.</li>\r\n<li>Any delivery dates provided to you in connection with order are estimates. The aim is to provide you with as accurate estimates as possible.</li>\r\n<li>Product that is delivered to you will be your responsibility from the completion of delivery. As soon as product delivered to you, you will be liable for any loss and damage to it thereafter. You must examine the product before accepting it.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>9. Changes and Cancellation</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>If you simply change your mind and without giving us a reason, you can cancel your order before product is paid; without incurring any liability. </li>\r\n<li>Once the payment was done, cancellation is not allowed. Although, you may change and return the product. </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>10. Return Policy</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Change Product<br/>We will not allow changing product due to change of mind unless it is factory damage once you receive.\r\nIf you wish to change the product is under factory damage once receive, kindly inform us and wait for further instruction.</li></ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>11. Excluding Liability</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The Company does not exclude liability for any fraudulent act or omission; or for death or personal injury caused by negligence or breach of the Company other obligation. Subject to this, the company is not liable for loss which is not reasonably foreseeable to both parties, or loss, or any loss of profit, loss of income, loss of business, loss of revenue, or loss of goodwill, or any loss of corruption of or damaged of date.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>12. General terms</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The contract will be solely between you, customer, and TAFFEN by the laws of Republic of the Philippines\r\nIf any provision of contract is not valid or legally enforceable, that the term will be deleted and the remaining terms will not be affected.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>', 'Terms and Conditions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'terms-and-conditions', '', '', '2016-05-15 11:08:23', '2016-05-15 11:08:23', '', 0, 'http://taffen.co/?page_id=66', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(376, 1, '2016-04-30 14:57:23', '2016-04-30 14:57:23', '<strong>Personal identification information</strong>\r\n\r\nWe may collect personal identification information from Users in a variety of ways, including, but not limited to, when Users visit our site, register on the siteplace an orderfill out a formsubscribe to the newsletter and in connection with other activities, services, features or resources we make available on our Site. Users may be asked for, as appropriate, name, email address, mailing address, phone number, credit card information,\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Users may, however, visit our Site anonymously.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe will collect personal identification information from Users only if they voluntarily submit such information to us. Users can always refuse to supply personally identification information, except that it may prevent them from engaging in certain Site related activities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Non-personal identification information</strong>\r\n\r\nWe may collect non-personal identification information about Users whenever they interact with our Site. Non-personal identification information may include the browser name, the type of computer and technical information about Users means of connection to our Site, such as the operating system and the Internet service providers utilized and other similar information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Web browser cookies</strong>\r\n\r\nOur Site may use “cookies” to enhance User experience. User’s web browser places cookies on their hard drive for record-keeping purposes and sometimes to track information about them. User may choose to set their web browser to refuse cookies, or to alert you when cookies are being sent. If they do so, note that some parts of the Site may not function properly.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How we use collected information</strong>\r\n\r\nTaffen collects and uses Users personal information for the following purposes:\r\n\r\nTo improve customer service\r\nYour information helps us to more effectively respond to your customer service requests and support needs.\r\nTo personalize user experience\r\nWe may use information in the aggregate to understand how our Users as a group use the services and resources provided on our Site.\r\nTo improve our Site\r\nWe continually strive to improve our website offerings based on the information and feedback we receive from you.\r\nTo process transactions\r\nWe may use the information Users provide about themselves when placing an order only to provide service to that order. We do not share this information with outside parties except to the extent necessary to provide the service.\r\nTo send periodic emails\r\n\r\nThe email address Users provide for order processing, will only be used to send them information and updates pertaining to their order. It may also be used to respond to their inquiries, and/or other requests or questions. If User decides to opt-in to our mailing list, they will receive emails that may include company news, updates, related product or service information, etc. If at any time the User would like to unsubscribe from receiving future emails, we include detailed unsubscribe instructions at the bottom of each email or User may contact us via our Site.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How we protect your information</strong>\r\n\r\nWe adopt appropriate data collection, storage and processing practices and security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction of your personal information, username, password, transaction information and data stored on our Site.\r\n\r\nSensitive and private data exchange between the Site and its Users happens over a SSL secured communication channel and is encrypted and protected with digital signatures.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Third party websites</strong>\r\nUsers may find advertising or other content on our Site that link to the sites and services of our partners, suppliers, advertisers, sponsors, licensors and other third parties. We do not control the content or links that appear on these sites and are not responsible for the practices employed by websites linked to or from our Site. In addition, these sites or services, including their content and links, may be constantly changing. These sites and services may have their own privacy policies and customer service policies. Browsing and interaction on any other website, including websites which have a link to our Site, is subject to that website\\’s own terms and policies.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Changes to this privacy policy</strong>\r\n\r\nTaffen has the discretion to update this privacy policy at any time. When we do, post a notification on the main page of our Site,revise the updated date at the bottom of this page,send you an email. We encourage Users to frequently check this page for any changes to stay informed about how we are helping to protect the personal information we collect. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this privacy policy periodically and become aware of modifications.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Your acceptance of these terms</strong>\r\n\r\nBy using this Site, you signify your acceptance of this policy and terms of service. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our Site. Your continued use of the Site following the posting of changes to this policy will be deemed your acceptance of those changes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Terms and Conditions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '66-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-30 14:57:23', '2016-04-30 14:57:23', '', 66, 'http://taffen.co/66-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
